Subject: Re:[VB] Starter won't turn over with key

  I have had similar problems from time to time with my 70 & 63 buses. The best fix is to put in a relay. This has worked for me eveer time. Modern vehicles have a relay to work the starter solenoid & this upgrade is fine if you are not am absolute purist type.
 
